My name is Tanya Blount I am a Licensed Massage Therapist (MT010942) and have been practicing in the field since 2011. I also am a Associated Bodywork and Massage Professional member specializing in Deep Tissue, Sports Massage, Hot Stone Massage as well as Therapeutic Massage Therapy.

Born in Augusta Georgia and raised in New England, I have always been a people person. I spent over 10 years in a corporate environment as a legal assistant but decided it was time for a change in 2009 when I decided to go to school for Massage Therapy. My passion to help others is what drove me to be a Massage Therapist.
